Executive Profile
Paul A. Hooper  Chief Executive Officer and Director, Gigamon Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships50$4,258,484As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Paul A. Hooper has been the Chief Executive Officer of Gigamon Inc. (formerly known as Gigamon LLC) since December 19, 2012. Mr. Hooper served as Vice President of Marketing at Gigamon Systems LLC. Mr. Hooper served as a Vice President of Marketing and Product Management at Gigamon Inc. from July 2011 to December 2012. He served as the Chief Marketing Officer of Extreme Networks Inc. from October 2009 to July 8, 2011 and served as its Vice President of Corporate ... Marketing until July 8, 2011. From November 1999 to August 2002, Mr. Hooper served in several positions, including Vice President of Information Technology at myCFO, Inc.,where he was responsible for the Enterprise Applications and Infrastructure for the fast-growing Financial Services and Advisory company. From March 1998 to November 1999, Mr. Hooper served as Senior Director of Information Technology at JDS Uniphase Corporation. From August 1996 to March 1998, Mr. Hooper served as a Senior Director of Networking and Telecommunications at Netscape Communications Corporation. Mr. Hooper served as Vice President and General Manager of Volume Products Group at Extreme Networks Inc. He was responsible for the strategy, product development and business management for Extreme Networks' Summit® family of fixed configuration switches, the BlackDiamond® 8800 family of modular switches, wireless LAN solution and security solutions. He was an Extreme Networks executive sponsor for data center and enterprise LAN initiatives. He served as Chief Information Officer of Extreme Networks Inc. from August 2002 to July 2011, where he oversaw Extreme Networks worldwide marketing efforts, where he led the strategic focus of solutions and technical marketing, global field marketing and corporate communications. Mr. Hooper oversaw the strategic use of IT systems and adherence to corporate compliance for data throughout a globally distributed business at Extreme Networks Inc. Specifically, he led the planning, procurement and ongoing support of business applications, network infrastructure and related services supporting more than 800 employees across 50 countries. Mr. Hooper has been a Director of Gigamon Inc. since December 19, 2012.Read Full Background




